data.description: Back on the market due to Buyer being an investor and deciding to purchase a different investment property that came back on the market.  Home Inspection came back clean with only minor updates needed, no structural or foundation, roofing or plumbing issues.  Appraisal Waiver was granted by the last Lender so home very likely to appraise moving forward.   NO HOA, NO CDD, Roof only 3 years old. Recently renovated in 2021 and estimated to be worth over 280k with a little TLC, this is your opportunity to own your very own home or add to your rental portfolio.   This spacious 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom property is located just 20 minutes from Tampa International Airport, and in close proximity to USF, Busch Gardens, and Adventure Island.    Featuring a nice backyard and a separate in unit laundry room, this two story property boasts a popular open concept and a spacious kitchen.  The upstairs entertainment loft is perfect for gamers,  2nd living room, or an office space. Envision the endless possibilities once you make this home your own.    Schedule your viewing today, this deal went off the market once, it won't last long!
